Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Unapred* sam ti rekao da nećeš uspeti. (I told you *in advance* that you wouldn't succeed.)
2. Planiram da uradim sve zadatke *unapred*. (I plan to do all the tasks *ahead* of time.)
3. Moramo da planiramo *unapred* da bismo izbegli probleme. (We need to plan *ahead* to avoid problems.)
4. Uputstvo je veoma jasno, tako da nećeš imati poteškoća da ga shvatiš *unapred*. (The instructions are very clear, so you won't have difficulty understanding them *in advance*.)
5. Učenik je čitao lekciju *unapred* pre nego što je došao u školu. (The student read the lesson *ahead* before coming to school.)
6. *Unapred* sam mu zahvalan na svim savetima koje mi je dao. (I am grateful to him *in advance* for all the advice he gave me.)
7. Razmislite o svim mogućim situacijama *unapred* kako biste bili spremni za sve što može da se desi. (Think about all possible situations *ahead* so you can be prepared for anything that may happen.)
8. Ovaj proizvod se može kupiti samo *unapred*. (This product can only be purchased *in advance*.)

I hope this helps!